name: DELICACY DICE CLAY
description: I happened to be at diner picking out some food to eat and on the menu I saw the word DELICACY and immediately Comedian Andrew "Dice" Clay came to mind and history was made. One of the first things that came to mind was that the first letter and last letter stayed exactly where they were, they didn't move. Why I saw DICE CLAY in the word DELICACY, who the hell knows. When your mind is wired a certain way, after awhile (if you're wise) you stop asking why and just accept it. Just accept yourself the way you are. Stop worrying about what other people might say or what they might be thinking. Life is way too short to give a hoot. If you spend your time thinking about what other people are saying, you're literally wasting your life away. Wait, how did this page turn into a Jay Shetty inspirational speech. lol
